  "content": "\n \n \n  <h3 data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <section data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n      <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n       <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"248\" data-backw=\"578\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"505080130\" data-ratio=\"0.4287037037037037\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8d588228-fcd3-4635-1dc5-b426cf26cd00/public\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8d588228-fcd3-4635-1dc5-b426cf26cd00/public\">\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section></h3>\n  <h3 style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <section data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n      <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n       <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin: -1.2em 8px 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\"></p>\n        <p style=\"margin: -1.2em 8px 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-family: inherit;font-size: 1em;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:inherit;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:inherit;\">新智元报道&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section></h3>\n  <section style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\">编辑：LRST</span>\n  </section>\n  <section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n     <h5 style=\"padding:10px;margin:10px 8px 0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;max-width:100%;word-break:break-all !important;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">【新智元导读】</strong>人类通过课堂学习知识，并在实践中不断应用与创新。那么，多模态大模型（LMMs）能通过观看视频实现「课堂学习」吗？新加坡南洋理工大学S-Lab团队推出了Video-MMMU——全球首个评测视频知识获取能力的数据集，为AI迈向更高效的知识获取与应用开辟了新路径。</span></h5>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-top: 24px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">想象一下，你正在观看吴恩达老师的机器学习课程，视频讲解清晰、动画直观，你很快掌握了核心概念，并能在考试中灵活应用，人类对这个过程再熟悉不过。</span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">那么，如果AI也能这样学习呢？</span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"328\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"720\" data-imgfileid=\"505079608\" data-ratio=\"0.5842592592592593\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7ddd8a63-b0e9-4058-8d6b-1a9d0249a300/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1232\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7ddd8a63-b0e9-4058-8d6b-1a9d0249a300/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">图1 Video-MMMU提出知识获取的3大认知阶段</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这正是Video-MMMU试图回答的核心问题：AI能否通过观看视频获取并应用知识？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">对于多模态大模型（LMMs）来说，视频不仅是它们感知世界的窗口，更是获取知识的重要途径。南洋理工大学S-Lab团队推出Video-MMMU数据集是首个评测LMMs从多学科专业视频中提取、理解并运用知识能力的创新基准。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">通过Video-MMMU，我们不再满足于模型「看懂」视频，而是探索它能否真正「学会」视频中的新知识，并运用这些知识解决实际问题。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"194\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"441\" data-imgfileid=\"505079606\" data-ratio=\"0.34444444444444444\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bf9d3d58-963d-4c38-7377-d7ebdfb0e500/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1280\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bf9d3d58-963d-4c38-7377-d7ebdfb0e500/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">论文地址：https://arxiv.org/abs/2501.13826</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">开源代码：https://github.com/EvolvingLMMs-Lab/VideoMMMU</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">项目主页：https://videommmu.github.io/</span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">数据集：https://huggingface.co/datasets/lmms-lab/VideoMMMU</span></p>\n  <section autoid=\"1895\" data-style-type=\"0\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-bottom:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p>三大认知阶段：从感知到应用</p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-top: 24px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">教育学认为，学习是一个渐进的认知过程 [1]，而Video-MMMU正是围绕这个过程设计的，将学习新知识拆解为三个认知阶段：感知（Perception）、理解（Comprehension）和运用（Adaptation），系统评估模型在知识获取不同层次的能力。</span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">感知（Perception）——信息获取的起点，</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">模型需要从视频中提取关键信息，这是获取知识的基础。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"122\" data-imgfileid=\"505079605\" data-ratio=\"0.09537037037037037\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9ad8685a-6183-4791-11e9-d77c95014c00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1280\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9ad8685a-6183-4791-11e9-d77c95014c00/public\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">理解（Comprehension）——从感知到掌握，</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">模型不仅需要「看清」，还要理解知识的深层次含义。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"126\" data-imgfileid=\"505079619\" data-ratio=\"0.09814814814814815\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/04f3c168-acff-4ab4-bbb1-88e6f3271600/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1280\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/04f3c168-acff-4ab4-bbb1-88e6f3271600/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">运用（Adaptation）——真正的学以致用，</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">模型需要将从视频中学到的知识运用到全新的场景中。这是测试学习能力的最终环节。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"129\" data-imgfileid=\"505079609\" data-ratio=\"0.10092592592592593\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/16191a8b-79f3-4cc0-2f2e-00384fe3e000/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1280\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/16191a8b-79f3-4cc0-2f2e-00384fe3e000/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section autoid=\"1895\" data-style-type=\"0\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-bottom:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p>知识增益（∆knowledge）：衡量模型的能力提升</p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-top: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Video-MMMU 的另一大亮点在于设计了「知识增益」（∆knowledge）指标。这一创新不仅关注模型的「绝对能力」，更评估其在观看视频前后的在应用阶段的表现提升。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"352\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"720\" data-imgfileid=\"505079611\" data-ratio=\"0.6259259259259259\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/aee4a25c-89c0-4d75-1027-26b8fec9ce00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1150\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/aee4a25c-89c0-4d75-1027-26b8fec9ce00/public\"></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 14px;\">图2 模型通过观看视频，将原本无法解决的问题做对。「解题」的能力不是唯一的检验标准，能获取知识，并把原本做错的问题做对，也是一种重要的能力。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">与传统评测不同，Video-MMMU更关注模型是否能通过观看视频解决原本无法解答的问题。从Video-MMMU的角度，智能不仅仅是「解题」的能力，更是快速学习和应用新技能的能力。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">对于多模态大模型来说，视频就是它们的课堂。通过视频「上课」，模型可以获取新知识，并灵活应用于实际生活中的未知挑战，不仅是对「智能」概念的重新思考，更是迈向通用智能（AGI）的一次有趣探索。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Video-MMMU 的发布，为评估和改进LMMs的知识获取能力提供了全新视角。如果人类的课堂是学习的起点，那么 Video-MMMU 就是LMMs走向课堂的一扇大门。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section autoid=\"1895\" data-style-type=\"0\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-bottom:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p>数据集的独特性</p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-top: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Video-MMMU的独特之处在于首次将视频作为知识传播的核心渠道，从传统的视频场景理解转向视频内容的知识学习。数据集专注于高质量教育视频，平均时长506.2秒，覆盖多个学科领域。其问题平均长度达75.7字，远超其他基准，体现出高度专业性和挑战性。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"339\" data-backw=\"578\" data-height=\"720\" data-imgfileid=\"505079620\" data-ratio=\"0.587037037037037\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1b70beb4-b8bf-4bff-34ea-fecf7ea68800/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1227\" style=\"width: 79%;height: auto !important;flex-basis: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1b70beb4-b8bf-4bff-34ea-fecf7ea68800/public\"></p>\n  <section autoid=\"1895\" data-style-type=\"0\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-bottom:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p>数据集设计</p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-top: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Video-MMMU覆盖6大专业领域（艺术、商业、医学、科学、人文、工程）中的30个学科。数据集包含精心筛选的300个大学水平的教育视频和900个高质量的问答对。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"185\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"422\" data-imgfileid=\"505079612\" data-ratio=\"0.3296296296296296\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3651bac5-09ea-4911-9112-0dccfe440400/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1280\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3651bac5-09ea-4911-9112-0dccfe440400/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"720\" data-imgfileid=\"505079613\" data-ratio=\"0.9148665819567979\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1f240bdd-3f5e-4332-6c35-601f69a69c00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"787\" data-width=\"787\" style=\"width: 79%;height: auto !important;flex-basis: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1f240bdd-3f5e-4332-6c35-601f69a69c00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section autoid=\"1895\" data-style-type=\"0\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-bottom:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p>问题设计</p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-top: 24px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"424\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"720\" data-imgfileid=\"505079610\" data-ratio=\"0.7547169811320755\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e40ea826-6655-4d23-61e1-ce4df049f700/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"954\" data-width=\"954\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e40ea826-6655-4d23-61e1-ce4df049f700/public\"></p>\n  <h4 style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">感知阶段的问题类型</span></strong></span></h4>\n  <ul start=\"1\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">ASR（自动语音识别）：要求模型准确转录视频中的口述内容。示例：如上图中Art（左上）的例子。</span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">OCR（光学字符识别）：从公式、图表或手写笔记中提取关键细节。示例：如上图中Business（左下）的例子。</span>\n    </section></li>\n  </ul>\n  <h4 style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 24px 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">理解阶段的问题类型</span></strong></span></h4>\n  <ul start=\"1\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">概念理解（Concept Comprehension）：通过不定项选择题评估模型对视频中概念的理解。示例：如上图中Humanities（中上）的例子。</span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">解题方法理解（Problem-solving Strategy Comprehension）：在视频中演示的解决问题基础上，通过改变输入值测试模型是否掌握了解题方法。示例：如上图中Science（中下）的例子。</span>\n    </section></li>\n  </ul>\n  <h4 style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 24px 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">运用阶段的问题类型</span></strong></span></h4>\n  <ul start=\"1\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">案例分析（Case Study Analysis）：将视频中讲解的知识应用于新的实际情</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\">境。示例：如上图Medicine（右上）的例子。</span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\">解题方法运用（Problem-solving Strategy Adaptation）：将视频中演示的解决方法应用于实际</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">的问题。示例：如上图中Engineering（右下）的例子。</span>\n    </section></li>\n  </ul>\n  <section autoid=\"1895\" data-style-type=\"0\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-bottom:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p>实验结果分析</p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-top: 24px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"357\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"720\" data-imgfileid=\"505079617\" data-ratio=\"0.6351851851851852\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1b7393d2-cffc-445f-28c3-173f46237500/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1133\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1b7393d2-cffc-445f-28c3-173f46237500/public\"></p>\n  <h4 style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 24px 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">各认知阶段的表现</span></strong></span></h4>\n  <ol start=\"1\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\">人类 vs. AI：人类专家在所有阶段的表现都优于模型，尽管Claude-3.5-Sonnet在模型中得分最高，但仍明显落后于人类。</span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\">难度逐级递增：无论是人类还是AI，从感知到理解再到运用，准确率逐步下降，说明越深层次的认知任务对能力要求越高。</span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\">知识</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">运用的挑战：运用阶段（Adaptation Track） 是知识获取的最大瓶颈，模型得分普遍低于50%。这表明，尽管模型在可能表面理解了视频知识，但在实际应用时仍存在明显短板，难以灵活迁移和运用所学内容。</span>\n    </section></li>\n  </ol>\n  <h4 style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 24px 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">音频文本的影响</span></strong></span></h4>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">作者使用 OpenAI Whisper 生成音频转录文本，以测试其对模型表现的影响。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"382\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"720\" data-imgfileid=\"505079615\" data-ratio=\"0.6792452830188679\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/24278f81-b13e-41e3-180e-a9e432c43e00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1060\" data-width=\"1060\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/24278f81-b13e-41e3-180e-a9e432c43e00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">结果显示：</span>\n  </section>\n  <ul start=\"1\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">感知与理解阶段：音频文本有助于模型更精准地理解视频内容，提高表现。</span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">运用阶段的挑战：模型表现反而下降，可能因为音频中存在冗余信息，干扰了模型对关键知识的提取和迁移能力。这说明，尽管音频文本能帮助AI“听懂”视频，但真正的知识应用依然是重大挑战。</span>\n    </section></li>\n  </ul>\n  <h3 style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 24px 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">知识增益的定量分析</span></strong></span></h3>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Video-MMMU 的核心创新之一是引入「知识增益」指标（∆knowledge）用于评估模型通过观看视频学习新知识的能力。与传统评测不同，该指标关注模型是否能通过视频学习，解决原本不会的问题，而不仅仅是静态的解题能力。（∆knowledge）定义为：</span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"107\" data-backw=\"578\" data-height=\"236\" data-imgfileid=\"505079621\" data-ratio=\"0.18425925925925926\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/cfad8d0d-806c-4beb-4f5b-5986ca85ef00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1280\" style=\"width: 57%;height: auto !important;flex-basis: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/cfad8d0d-806c-4beb-4f5b-5986ca85ef00/public\"></p>\n  <h4 style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">人类 vs. AI：学习能力差距</span></strong></h4>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-top: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">人类在观看视频后，知识增益达33.1%，而表现最好的模型（GPT-4o）仅为15.6%，多数模型低于10%。更令人意外的是，一些模型在观看视频后反而表现下降，表明它们在知识学习和应用方面仍远不及人类。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"276\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"629\" data-imgfileid=\"505079616\" data-ratio=\"0.49166666666666664\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7c3bd3e2-66da-4a62-688a-6ecba235f300/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1280\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7c3bd3e2-66da-4a62-688a-6ecba235f300/public\">\n  </section>\n  <h3 style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">模型的知识获取两面性</span></strong></span></h3>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">仅凭知识增益（∆knowledge）并不能全面衡量模型的真实学习能力。因此，作者进一步引入两个关键指标：</span>\n  </section>\n  <ul start=\"1\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">错误转正确率（Wrong-to-Right Rate）：模型能否通过视频学习，把原本错误的答案修正？定义为：</span></p></li>\n  </ul>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"85\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"194\" data-imgfileid=\"505079614\" data-ratio=\"0.15185185185185185\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c35117ad-d493-4652-9f0c-11c16c743600/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1280\" style=\"width: 77%;height: auto !important;flex-basis: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c35117ad-d493-4652-9f0c-11c16c743600/public\">\n  </section>\n  <ul start=\"1\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">正确转错误率（Right-to-Wrong Rate）：模型是否看视频之后，把原本做对的题做错了？</span></p></li>\n  </ul>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"273\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"621\" data-imgfileid=\"505079618\" data-ratio=\"0.48518518518518516\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fa2dda7f-0887-44b2-a735-ac7bce25cd00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1280\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fa2dda7f-0887-44b2-a735-ac7bce25cd00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">实验发现，大多数模型取得较为不错的错误转正确率，显示出一定的学习能力。但是，大多数模型的正确转错误率远高于人类，表明它们在吸收视频知识时仍存在明显不足。</span>\n  </section>\n  <h3 style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">人类的认知优势</span></strong></span></h3>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">人类在这两个指标上的表现更加平衡：</span>\n  </section>\n  <ul start=\"1\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">错误转正确率：40.4% → 说明人类能更有效地学习新知识。</span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">正确转错误率：10.7% → 这表明，人类能够自然整合新旧知识，而模型在处理视频信息时，往往会修改原本正确的答案，这成为其学习能力的核心短板之一。</span></p></li>\n  </ul>\n  <section autoid=\"1895\" data-style-type=\"0\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-bottom:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p>结论：模型的瓶颈</p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-top: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">实验结果揭示了当前多模态大模型（LMMs）在视频学习中的两大挑战：</span></p>\n  <ol start=\"1\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">学习能力有限：难以高效获取并应用新知识。</span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">模型回答的不稳定性：原本会做的题，看完视频后反而不会了。</span>\n    </section></li>\n  </ol>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如何提升LMMs的学习效率和稳定性，将是提升视频知识获取能力的关键。</span>\n  </section>\n  <h3 style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">错误分析</span></strong></span></h3>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">作者对Claude-3.5-Sonnet在运用阶段的100个错误进行了分类，分析模型做错的根本原因。</span>\n  </section>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"353\" data-backw=\"578\" data-height=\"720\" data-imgfileid=\"505079622\" data-ratio=\"0.6111111111111112\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f7b15163-9342-4282-b9e5-b6e18398ec00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1179\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f7b15163-9342-4282-b9e5-b6e18398ec00/public\"></p>\n  <ul start=\"1\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">方法选择错误（8%）：模型选择了错误的解题方法，也就是说，它未能理解视频中讲解的正确策略。简单来说，模型看了视频，但没有选对路。</span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">方法运用错误（64%）：这是最常见的错误。模型记住了视频中的方法，但在新情境下无法灵活应用。比如，它理解了视频中的解题方法，但无法正确运用到另一个场景中。</span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">问题误读错误（15%）：模型没读懂题目，比如错看了数值或条件。这些错误和知识获取无关，更像是「粗心大意」。</span></p></li>\n  </ul>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">作者详细分析了模型方法运用错误的例子：</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"414\" data-backw=\"578\" data-height=\"720\" data-imgfileid=\"505079623\" data-ratio=\"0.7164179104477612\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bd93c657-bc7c-4504-6e39-35651df47700/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1005\" data-width=\"1005\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bd93c657-bc7c-4504-6e39-35651df47700/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section autoid=\"1895\" data-style-type=\"0\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-bottom:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p>总结</p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-top: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Video-MMMU首次系统性评测了LMMs从视频中学习、理解和应用知识的能力，揭示了当前多模态大模型在学习效率和知识迁移上的显著不足。提升模型从视频中获取知识的能力，将是迈向AGI的重要一步。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\">参考资料：</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\">[1] Mary Forehand. Bloom’s taxonomy. Emerging perspectives on learning, teaching, and technology, 41(4):47–56, 2010</span></section>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "南洋理工和 CMU 发布 Video-MMMU，全球首个评估多模态大模型视频学习能力并衡量知识增益的基准数据集。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "南洋理工和 CMU 发布 Video-MMMU，全球首个评估多模态大模型视频学习能力并衡量知识增益的基准数据集。",
  "summary": "Video-MMMU 是南洋理工大学和 CMU 联合推出的全球首个用于评测多模态大模型 (LMMs) 从视频中获取知识能力的数据集。该数据集通过模拟人类课堂学习，将知识获取分为感知、理解和运用三个认知阶段，并设计了独特的“知识增益”指标，用于评估模型通过观看视频解决问题的能力提升。该数据集覆盖 6 大专业领域(艺术、商业、医学、科学、人文、工程)中的 30 个学科。实验结果表明，当前 LMMs 在视频学习中面临学习效率低和稳定性差的挑战，尤其在知识运用方面与人类存在显著差距，例如在“错误转正确率”和“正确转错误率”上。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Video-MMMU 数据集是首个评测 LMMs 从视频中学习能力的数据集。",
      "explanation": "该数据集专注于评估模型从多学科专业视频中提取、理解并运用知识的能力，填补了该领域的空白。"
    },
    {
      "point": "知识增益指标能有效衡量模型通过观看视频后的能力提升。",
      "explanation": "该指标关注模型是否能通过视频学习解决原本无法解答的问题，更全面地评估了模型的学习效果。"
    },
    {
      "point": "LMMs 在知识运用阶段表现不佳，且模型回答的稳定性有待提高，在错误转正确率和正确转错误率上与人类的学习能力存在差距。",
      "explanation": "实验表明，LMMs 在知识运用阶段表现不佳，且模型回答的稳定性有待提高，在错误转正确率和正确转错误率上与人类的学习能力存在差距。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "通过 Video-MMMU， 我们不再满足于模型「看懂」视频， 而是探索它能否真正「学会」视频中的新知识， 并运用这些知识解决实际问题。",
    "从 Video-MMMU 的角度， 智能不仅仅是「解题」的能力， 更是快速学习和应用新技能的能力。",
    "如果人类的课堂是学习的起点， 那么 Video-MMMU 就是 LMMs 走向课堂的一扇大门。"
  ],
